title: Omelette
content:
Omelette is a category of item. It can be cooked in The Delectable Dab Kitchen in Hopeport using the Chef profession. Recipes for the Chef profession can be found in the Chef Recipe Book. Omelettes can be sold to Head Chef.


 * Basic Omelette
 * Appetizing Omelette
 * Tasty Omelette
 * Delicious Omelette
 * Gourmet Omelette
